strings: <voice_0x01000F25><se_low>*: Well! You're lookin' mighty pleased with yourself, Your Majesty. How'd you fare in the initiation?

<voice_0x01000F26><se_def>Prince Charmles: Oh, it was a mere formality!
See! I would have got a larger one, but I'm far too busy to waste my time on such fripperies!
<voice_0x01000F27><se_low>*: Wha..!? That's the biggest Argon heart I ever did see! You mean to say you defeated the lizard that had this all by yourself?
